name: Interplanetary (itch) (Mistereee)
description:
Explore an infinitely expanding universe in this "No Man's Sky" like game.

Use your mouse to move the ship and interact with the world.

After getting shot down while trying to escape the authorities you are left with only an escape pod.

Made in 7 days for the boundless game jam: https://itch.io/jam/boundless-game-jam
